1
00:01:29,690 --> 00:01:33,170
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,650 --> 00:01:36,200
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:36,520 --> 00:01:37,990
Mr. Liu threatened me,

4
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,570
saying that witnessing this

5
00:01:39,570 --> 00:01:41,170
would surely bring me death.

6
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,479
If I wanted to stay alive,

7
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:44,080
I had to do exactly as he said.

8
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,160
My Lady,

9
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,840
I truly feared death,

10
00:01:47,330 --> 00:01:49,850
so I had no choice
but to hide the truth from you.

11
00:01:49,850 --> 00:01:51,170
Is what you said true?

12
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:55,120
It was my father who killed Nian'an.

13
00:01:55,440 --> 00:01:58,509
My Lady,
this is a matter of great importance.

14
00:01:58,530 --> 00:02:01,370
I can only tell you exactly
what I saw and heard.

15
00:02:02,270 --> 00:02:04,010
As for the truth,

16
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:06,570
I dare not make any reckless assumptions.

17
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,560
What do you mean ''reckless assumptions''?

18
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,759
Isn't it obvious?

19
00:02:14,780 --> 00:02:15,820
I never thought

20
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:20,720
that the culprit who killed my husband

21
00:02:21,550 --> 00:02:23,210
would actually be my father.

22
00:02:33,329 --> 00:02:36,310
I have failed you, Nian'an.

23
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:39,090
My Lady! My Lady!

24
00:02:39,490 --> 00:02:41,160
My Lady, are you alright?

25
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:43,240
What's the point of ending your own life?

26
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,329
It might bring momentary relief
and put an end to everything,

27
00:02:45,329 --> 00:02:47,590
but Shen Nian'an would have died in vain.

28
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:49,710
Even if I'm resentful, what can I do?

29
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,600
He is my father.

30
00:02:51,650 --> 00:02:52,980
Your father killed him,

31
00:02:53,310 --> 00:02:54,950
and made you marry a monster.

32
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:56,740
Are you willing to be manipulated by him
for the rest of your life,

33
00:02:56,740 --> 00:02:58,000
living in the shadows?

34
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:59,360
Then what should I do?

35
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,970
You are yourself first.

36
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,850
Only then are you someone's wife,

37
00:03:02,850 --> 00:03:04,180
or someone's daughter.

38
00:03:04,690 --> 00:03:05,490
Remember:

39
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,670
For your own sake,

40
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:08,780
the edge of your blade

41
00:03:08,780 --> 00:03:10,580
should be firmly aimed outward.

42
00:03:11,320 --> 00:03:13,380
Make those who ruined your happiness

43
00:03:14,210 --> 00:03:15,530
pay the price.

44
00:03:17,540 --> 00:03:18,710
For myself?

45
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:19,790
Yes.

46
00:03:20,329 --> 00:03:21,210
For yourself.

47
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:25,480
Weakness and submission only make
the wicked more unscrupulous.

48
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:26,390
Jingjing.

49
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,500
Stand up when you're done crying.

50
00:03:28,670 --> 00:03:30,440
Take the knife they gave you

51
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:32,750
and strike hard at their weak spots.

52
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,800
Exactly.

53
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,280
I want revenge.

54
00:03:45,100 --> 00:03:47,880
[Prime Minister's Mansion]

55
00:03:49,530 --> 00:03:50,329
Father.

56
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,079
The Lantern Festival is coming soon.

57
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,440
I would like to go to the temple
to pray for blessings.

58
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:56,640
Pray for blessings?

59
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,880
Why?

60
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,920
Father, I have figured it out.

61
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,040
Some things are already set in stone.

62
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,760
Let the past be the past.

63
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,710
It is time to put an end to this.

64
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:08,600
I agree to the marriage
you arranged for me.

65
00:04:08,730 --> 00:04:10,690
So I want to visit the temple,

66
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,920
consider it fulfilling a vow
on your behalf.

67
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:15,600
Jingjing, I'm glad you've come around.

68
00:04:17,370 --> 00:04:20,769
Father, after all,
this is my marriage to Mr. Liu,

69
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,840
I would like to invite him to join me.

70
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,640
All right.

71
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,080
Jingjing has finally changed her mind.

72
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:29,840
I'll leave this matter for you to handle.

73
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,280
Yes.

74
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,280
I will go right away.

75
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:53,900
Hey.

76
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,480
Why did we stop?

77
00:04:55,750 --> 00:05:00,550
[Tea]

78
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,310
Mr. Liu, my lady is thirsty,

79
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:00,750
and wants to go in for some tea.

80
00:05:00,750 --> 00:05:01,630
Tea?

81
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,690
Aren't we almost there?

82
00:05:03,690 --> 00:05:07,570
[Tea]

83
00:05:03,850 --> 00:05:05,210
My lady feels a bit tight in the chest.

84
00:05:05,210 --> 00:05:06,560
There happens to be a teahouse here.

85
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:08,690
She'd like to take a short rest inside.

86
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:11,570
Fine.

87
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,360
Hmph.

88
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:15,700
[Tea]

89
00:05:16,930 --> 00:05:19,910
I think I've been to this teahouse before.

90
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:27,680
Jingjing?

91
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,480
Jingjing?

92
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,080
Jingjing?

93
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,800
Hey.

94
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,400
Where did she go?

95
00:05:46,300 --> 00:05:46,700
You...

96
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,640
Who are you?

97
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,540
Seems you recovered from that hit

98
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,360
pretty quickly.

99
00:05:57,770 --> 00:05:58,690
Oh.

100
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,470
It was you that night.

101
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:01,800
Just you wait.

102
00:06:08,810 --> 00:06:09,740
Get out of my way!

103
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:10,990
Do you know who I am?

104
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:12,220
Who are you?

105
00:06:12,400 --> 00:06:14,400
A lackey sucking up to the powerful.

106
00:06:14,650 --> 00:06:16,200
A freeloading son-in-law.

107
00:06:16,470 --> 00:06:17,350
Or perhaps,

108
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,760
you're both.

109
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:19,920
What are you talking about?

110
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,210
I-I don't understand.

111
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,760
But you had better know this:

112
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:25,310
My wife is the Prime Minister's daughter!

113
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,570
This is the capital.

114
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,880
How dare you commit violence here?

115
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:30,540
Commit violence?

116
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,220
It seems you've forgotten

117
00:06:32,220 --> 00:06:35,680
how Shen Nian'an was killed by you here.

118
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,680
You are talking nonsense!

119
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:48,320
If you don't want anyone to know,

120
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,950
don't do it in the first place.

121
00:06:49,950 --> 00:06:51,360
Did you really think you could cover up

122
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:54,280
what you've done?

123
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:57,480
How could you possibly know?

124
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,340
Could it be that bitch Yang?

125
00:07:11,670 --> 00:07:12,740
Nian'an,

126
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:16,000
if your spirit is watching from heaven,

127
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:17,360
watch closely.

128
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:20,680
Today,

129
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:23,720
justice will be served for you!

130
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:28,830
Please let me go.

131
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:30,200
Please.

132
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,200
Let you go?

133
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:34,080
You will die the exact same way

134
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:35,560
Shen Nian'an did.

135
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:36,560
No.

136
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:39,190
You'll pay back double.

137
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,960
You've got it wrong.

138
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:43,620
I didn't kill Shen Nian'an!

139
00:07:44,880 --> 00:07:45,520
It was

140
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,970
Prime Minister Lin

141
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:49,610
who insisted on killing him.

142
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:51,540
It has nothing to do with me!

143
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:54,190
Shen Nian'an was Prime Minister Lin's
honored son-in-law.

144
00:07:54,190 --> 00:07:55,440
For no reason,

145
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:58,159
why would he kill Shen Nian'an?

146
00:07:58,440 --> 00:08:00,480
You must have instigated

147
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:02,000
and bewitched the Prime Minister Lin.

148
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:03,160
That's not true.

149
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,120
That's not true.

150
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,520
Shen Nian'an

151
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,630
was investigating Lingya Tower

152
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,640
and found out

153
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:11,130
that Prime Minister Lin was involved.

154
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:18,280
What is the relation between
Prime Minister Lin and Lingya Tower?

155
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:20,520
I don't know!

156
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:25,720
All I know is

157
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:29,880
that Prime Minister Lin has always
had dealings with Lingya Tower.

158
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,920
Many officials in the court

159
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:34,240
were also introduced
by Prime Minister Lin.

160
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,559
I knew this matter involved many people,

161
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:39,400
so I kept advising Shen Nian'an

162
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,720
not to dig any deeper.

163
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,640
But he wouldn't listen,

164
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:45,520
insisted on handling it impartially.

165
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:50,360
You know how to wash your hands of guilt,
don't you?

166
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:52,480
Shen Nian'an investigating Lingya Tower,

167
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,640
if no one had reported it,

168
00:08:53,640 --> 00:08:55,360
how would Prime Minister Lin have known?

169
00:08:55,360 --> 00:08:57,280
You must have sold him out

170
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:59,110
to curry favor with Prime Minister Lin.

171
00:08:59,110 --> 00:09:00,440
No, it wasn't like that.

172
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,600
Listen to me.

173
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:04,060
Prime Minister Lin has eyes and ears
all over the court.

174
00:09:04,060 --> 00:09:06,120
How could Shen Nian'an's investigation

175
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:08,000
possibly escape his notice?

176
00:09:08,380 --> 00:09:09,770
Think about it, right?

177
00:09:09,860 --> 00:09:13,250
Prime Minister Lin found out
that Shen Nian'an held

178
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,610
a detailed ledger of

179
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:17,640
the gold flowing into Lingya Tower.

180
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,840
That's why he came to me,

181
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:22,040
wanting my help to get the ledger.

182
00:09:22,230 --> 00:09:23,070
Oh.

183
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:27,220
So it was you

184
00:09:27,610 --> 00:09:29,680
who tricked Shen Nian'an into coming here

185
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,330
and forced him to hand over the ledger.

186
00:09:31,330 --> 00:09:32,490
Where is the ledger now?

187
00:09:32,490 --> 00:09:35,080
Of course Prime Minister Lin took it.

188
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:38,880
It seems keeping you alive is useless.

189
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:41,620
Wait, wait! No, no, no!

190
00:09:41,650 --> 00:09:43,150
Don't kill me.

191
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,120
I know where the thing you want is.

192
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:52,210
Inside Prime Minister Lin's room,

193
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:54,020
there is a secret chamber.

194
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,230
Shen Nian'an's ledger

195
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,200
is kept right there!

196
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,320
The sound from this wall is strange.

197
00:10:18,340 --> 00:10:20,820
The secret chamber must be right here.

198
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,520
Master, look.

199
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:31,100
There are scratches on it.

200
00:10:36,430 --> 00:10:37,580
The secret chamber.

201
00:10:48,860 --> 00:10:51,920
Why are there so many gold coins
from Lingya Tower here?

202
00:10:58,690 --> 00:10:59,490
Ah!

203
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:01,640
[Blueprint Collection of Lingya Tower]

204
00:10:59,750 --> 00:11:00,550
This...

205
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:03,170
[Patterns]

206
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,710
[Gate] [Fence]

207
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:07,900
This is the design draft my father drew
for Lingya Tower years ago.

208
00:11:15,530 --> 00:11:17,180
It really is him.

209
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:21,150
What's wrong, Master?

210
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,150
Every noble who enters Lingya Tower

211
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,860
has their own unique mask.

212
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:28,720
And this one belongs to Hei Ya.

213
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:30,630
Are you saying

214
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:35,020
that Prime Minister Lin is Hei Ya?

215
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,880
Yes.

216
00:11:51,190 --> 00:11:52,150
Heroine.

217
00:11:52,970 --> 00:11:54,690
I wasn't lying, was I?

218
00:11:55,560 --> 00:11:58,280
I was truly forced into this.

219
00:11:58,680 --> 00:12:01,560
Please let me go.

220
00:12:06,070 --> 00:12:08,550
Jingjing, why is it you?

221
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:10,130
Every single thing you did

222
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,330
and every single word you said,

223
00:12:12,370 --> 00:12:13,770
I heard it all.

224
00:12:13,790 --> 00:12:14,750
Jingjing.

225
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:17,360
It's not what it sounded like.

226
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:20,020
What I said today was just
an expedient measure.

227
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:22,020
If my life wasn't at stake,

228
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,160
I would never have done this.

229
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,920
I thought you were just a hypocrite,

230
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,200
a power-hungry sycophant.

231
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,800
But I didn't expect

232
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,010
you to bite the hand that feeds you.

233
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,680
You are worse than a beast!

234
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:36,320
Jingjing,

235
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:37,480
listen to me.

236
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,300
Liu Yuan.

237
00:12:38,670 --> 00:12:41,530
You can treat me as a stepping stone
to your success.

238
00:12:42,570 --> 00:12:44,100
But your fatal mistake

239
00:12:44,810 --> 00:12:46,840
was harming my Nian'an.

240
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,680
Today,

241
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:54,130
I will avenge my Nian'an
with my own hands.

242
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:01,340
Master.

243
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,480
The death match for the Lantern Festival

244
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,080
is fully prepared.

245
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:06,860
Bets can be opened at any time.

246
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:10,020
No rush.
Our honored guests have yet to arrive.

247
00:13:10,490 --> 00:13:11,490
Wait a bit longer.

248
00:13:11,760 --> 00:13:12,240
Yes.

